  "explanation": "The defendant is a first-time offender who embezzled a relatively modest sum and has demonstrated remorse by making partial restitution. While embezzlement is a serious breach of trust, a 10-year sentence suggested by the spectator is disproportionate to both the scale of the crime and the defendant's clean record. A sentence of 6 months incarceration is sufficient to provide a punitive deterrent while allowing for rehabilitation.",
